               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3624"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__ulrich_haringseer_QGW_II_II_3554">Ulreich Haringseer,
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> zu
                        Wienn</rs>,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">bestätigt</triggerstring>, <rs type="fn" role="recipient">von
                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_teschler_QGW_II_II_2951">Niclasen
                        Teschler, des <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">rats</roleName> der
                        stat zu Wienn</rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="pe__thomas_egkenperger_QGW_II_II_3455">Thoman Ekkenperger, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> daselbs, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">verweser</roleName> der stat gruntpücher,
                           <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__johann_wilhalm_QGW_II_II_3554">zu
                              <add>handen</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__niklas_wilhalm_QGW_II_II_3555">
                           <add>zu handen</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__servatius_humel_QGW_II_II_3556">
                           <add>zu handen</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__anna_QGW_II_II_3556_b">
                           <add>zu handen</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_II_3556">
                           <add>zu handen</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__christine_QGW_II_II_3556">
                           <add>zu handen</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__johann_humel_QGW_II_II_3556">
                           <add>zu handen</add></roleName></rs></rs> Hannsen und Niclasen,
                  geprüdern, der Wilhalm zu Haringsee, und Zirvosen, Annen, Margreten, Kristein und
                  Hennslein, fraun Kathrein, Michels Humel witiben, kindern und irer miterben, die
                  in der stat saczpuch geschriben stent, handen <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II"><measure>100 lb dn.</measure>, <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3624_men_1"><rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II">die
                                 <measure><add>100 lb dn.</add></measure></rs>
                        <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__leonhard_lehenholzer_QGW_II_II_3371">Lienhart
                              Lehenholczer</rs></rs>
                        <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I">von <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_alter_fleischmarkt_3"><roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__leonhard_lehenholzer_QGW_II_II_3371">seins</roleName>
                              hauss wegen, <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-alter_fleischmarkt">am Alten Fleischmarkt
                                 gelegen</roleName></rs>,</rs> das er <rs type="fn" role="issuer">von <rs type="person" ref="pe__ulrich_haringseer_QGW_II_II_3554">in</rs></rs>
                        <triggerstring n="disp">gekaufft</triggerstring>,</rs> zu der stat gruntpuch
                     erlegt hat,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">erhalten zu haben</triggerstring>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3624"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Besiegelt mit
